text.div: <xml-fragment mediaType="text/x-hl7-text+xml"> <urn:br xmlns:urn="urn:hl7-org:v3"/> <urn:br xmlns:urn="urn:hl7-org:v3"/> <urn:br xmlns:urn="urn:hl7-org:v3"/>To contact a local service within 2 hours (Dx05) Selected service: DO NOT BOOK APPOINTMENT - TESTING Whitchurch Minor Injury Unit</xml-fragment>

<xml-fragment mediaType="text/x-hl7-text+xml"> <urn:br xmlns:urn="urn:hl7-org:v3"/> <urn:br xmlns:urn="urn:hl7-org:v3"/> <urn:br xmlns:urn="urn:hl7-org:v3"/> <urn:br xmlns:urn="urn:hl7-org:v3"/> <urn:br xmlns:urn="urn:hl7-org:v3"/>InjuryBite or stingInsect or spider biteSting/bite more than 6 hours agoVery severe, deep limb pain</xml-fragment>

<xml-fragment mediaType="text/x-hl7-text+xml"> <urn:br xmlns:urn="urn:hl7-org:v3"/> <urn:br xmlns:urn="urn:hl7-org:v3"/> <urn:br xmlns:urn="urn:hl7-org:v3"/> <urn:br xmlns:urn="urn:hl7-org:v3"/> <urn:br xmlns:urn="urn:hl7-org:v3"/> <urn:br xmlns:urn="urn:hl7-org:v3"/> <urn:br xmlns:urn="urn:hl7-org:v3"/> <urn:br xmlns:urn="urn:hl7-org:v3"/> <urn:br xmlns:urn="urn:hl7-org:v3"/> <urn:br xmlns:urn="urn:hl7-org:v3"/> <urn:br xmlns:urn="urn:hl7-org:v3"/> <urn:br xmlns:urn="urn:hl7-org:v3"/> <urn:br xmlns:urn="urn:hl7-org:v3"/> <urn:br xmlns:urn="urn:hl7-org:v3"/> <urn:br xmlns:urn="urn:hl7-org:v3"/> <urn:br xmlns:urn="urn:hl7-org:v3"/> <urn:br xmlns:urn="urn:hl7-org:v3"/> <urn:br xmlns:urn="urn:hl7-org:v3"/>An injury or health problem was the reason for the contact.Heavy bleeding had not occurred in the previous 2 hours.An injury or symptom relating to an injury was the main problem.User Comments: TESTThere was a minor injury (a bite or sting).User Comments: TESTPathway selected - Bites and StingsThe bite or sting was caused by an insect or spider.User Comments: TESTThe sting/bite had not occurred within the previous 6 hours.The individual had been stung less than 10 timesThe individual was not experiencing nausea and/or vomiting.The sting did not involve the eyes, mouth or limb.There was no insect/insect part remaining attached to the skinThere was very severe, deep pain.Instructions given were: The individual needs to contact a local service within 2 hours.Directory of Services referral: DO NOT BOOK APPOINTMENT - TESTING Whitchurch Minor Injury UnitAdvice given: Worsening </xml-fragment>

<xml-fragment mediaType="text/x-hl7-text+xml"> <urn:br xmlns:urn="urn:hl7-org:v3"/> <urn:br xmlns:urn="urn:hl7-org:v3"/>If there are any new symptoms, or if the condition gets worse, changes or you have any other concerns, call us back.</xml-fragment>

<xml-fragment mediaType="text/x-hl7-text+xml"> <urn:content styleCode="bold" xmlns:urn="urn:hl7-org:v3">Note:</urn:content> <urn:br xmlns:urn="urn:hl7-org:v3"/> <urn:content xmlns:urn="urn:hl7-org:v3">TEST NOTE West Midlands Single Instance</urn:content> <urn:br xmlns:urn="urn:hl7-org:v3"/> <urn:br xmlns:urn="urn:hl7-org:v3"/>Special Notes from an external system were flagged as being present for this patient.</xml-fragment>
